<plot>A reality sitcom with a difference that follows the everyday lives of a group of six strangers who move into a London flat for eight weeks. The difference is that three of the flatmates are not what they seem and are, in fact, actors under the control of a team of writers living nearby. The writers follow the script of various contrived situations to see how far they can push the situation without being discovered by the flatmates.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063041</url></doc>
